    • Field Detail

      • BUILDING_ID_REFERENCE_NAME

        public static final java.lang.String BUILDING_ID_REFERENCE_NAME
        Name used to get building identifier references.

        Use DiscoveryRequest.addReference(String) to be able to retrieve the building identifier from the returned PlaceLink (using PlaceLink.getReference(String) ).

        The building identifier can also be retrieved using PlaceRequest.addReference(String) and Place.getReference(String).

        See Also:
        Places (Search) API Developer's Guide, DiscoveryRequest.addReference(String), PlaceLink.getReference(String), PlaceRequest.addReference(String), Place.getReference(String), Constant Field Values
        Product:
        nlp-hybrid-plus

      • PVID_ID_REFERENCE_NAME

        Places (Search) API Developer's Guide, DiscoveryRequest.addReference(String), PlaceLink.getReference(String), PlaceRequest.addReference(String), Place.getReference(String), Constant Field Values

      • VENUES_ID_REFERENCE_NAME

        public static final java.lang.String VENUES_ID_REFERENCE_NAME
        Name used to get all venues identifier references.

        Use DiscoveryRequest.addReference(String) to be able to retrieve all venues identifier from the returned PlaceLink (using PlaceLink.getReference(String) ).

        The venues identifier can also be retrieved using PlaceRequest.addReference(String) and Place.getReference(String).

        This reference name can be used retrieve all the different venues identifiers, namely: VENUES_CONTENT_ID_REFERENCE_NAME, VENUES_DESTINATION_ID_REFERENCE_NAME and VENUES_VENUE_ID_REFERENCE_NAME.

        See Also:
        Places (Search) API Developer's Guide, DiscoveryRequest.addReference(String), PlaceLink.getReference(String), PlaceRequest.addReference(String), Place.getReference(String), Constant Field Values

      • VENUES_CONTENT_ID_REFERENCE_NAME

        public static final java.lang.String VENUES_CONTENT_ID_REFERENCE_NAME
        Name used to get only venues.content identifier references.

        See Also:
        Places (Search) API Developer's Guide, DiscoveryRequest.addReference(String), PlaceLink.getReference(String), PlaceRequest.addReference(String), Place.getReference(String), Constant Field Values

      • PLACE_CONTENT_WIKIPEDIA

        public static final java.lang.String PLACE_CONTENT_WIKIPEDIA
        Name used to get editorial wikipedia content in place details response.
